    "body": "I got bitten by this bug [today](https://twitter.com/vrde/status/1362058886740647945), and it took me quite some time (and help from others) to find out the culprit.\r\n\r\nI guess it takes some time to fix the bug properly, in the meantime may I suggest to **hide** the `Gas limit` input when the user is connected to `Web3 Provider` or `Injected Web3`? That would help users to avoid those kind of mistakes.\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/134680/108244724-cb2cd480-714f-11eb-810d-f378efb1988f.png)\r\n\r\nThanks :)",
